<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ceza Hukuku - Gürr & Duru Hukuk Bürosu</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Ceza Hukuku</h1>
        
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Ceza Hukuku Hizmetlerimiz</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    Gürr & Duru Hukuk Bürosu olarak, ceza hukuku alanında profesyonel ve kapsamlı hizmet sunmaktayız. Deneyimli ekibimiz, soruşturma aşamasından yargılama sürecine kadar tüm aşamalarda müvekkillerimizin haklarını korumaktadır.
                </p>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Soruşturma Aşaması</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>İfade alma işlemleri</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Gözaltı sürecinde hukuki destek</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Sulh ceza hakimliği işlemleri</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Tutuklama ve tahliye talepleri</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Kovuşturma Aşaması</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Duruşma temsili</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Delil toplama ve değerlendirme</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Savunma hazırlama</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>İstinaf ve temyiz başvuruları</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Özel Ceza Hukuku</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Ekonomik suçlar</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Siber suçlar</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Uyuşturucu suçları</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Organize suçlar</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">İnfaz Hukuku</h3>
                        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Ceza infaz kurumu işlemleri</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Denetimli serbestlik işlemleri</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>Koşullu salıverilme talepleri</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start">
                                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                                <span>İnfaz hesaplamaları</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Savunma İlkelerimiz</h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Adil Yargılanma</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Etkin savunma hakkı</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Gizlilik</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Müvekkil bilgilerinin korunması</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Hızlı Müdahale</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">7/24 acil hukuki destek</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 